Comment: 0,0:00:00.18,0:00:00.18,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.55,0:23:27.71,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,哇 下雪了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.17,0:23:33.76,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 先被发现了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.80,0:23:35.39,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,我重来一次 NG　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.39,0:23:36.72,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,重来重来
